quran[51]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,"Twâ, sín, mîm"
  26,2,Oyo nde mikapo mia buku ya polele
  26,3,Ozali komitungisa mpo été baboyi kondima
  26,4,"Soki tolingaki mbele tokitisaki bilembo epai na bango kowuta о likolo, bakingo na bango elingaki kogumbama. (na soni)"
  26,5,"Мре tango nyoso lilendisi ya sika likoyela bango kowuta epai ya Ar-Rahmân, sé bakopesa yango mokongo"
  26,6,"Baboyaki kondima, (na makambo nyoso oyo ewutaki epai ya Nkolo wa bango) kala te bakoyelaka bango basango тропа maye bazalaki kotiola na yango"
  26,7,Boye bazali kornona mabele te boni tokolisaki kati na yango (milona mibale mibale) na lolenge ya malamu
  26,8,"Ya soló, wana ezali elembo. Kasi ebele kati na bango bazali kondima te"
  26,9,"Mpe ya soló, Nkolo wa yo azali wa bokasi atonda ngolu"
  26,10,"Mpe tango Nkolo wayo abengaki Mûssa, kende epai ya bato ya mabe"
  26,11,Bato ya falo. Bazali kobanga (Allah) te
  26,12,"Alobi: Nkolo, ya sólo nazali kobanga ete bandimela ngai te"
  26,13,"Ntolo na ngai ezali ya kokangama, mpe lolemu na ngai elobaka malamu te, tinda yango epai ya Hâruna"
  26,14,"Mpe nazali na mabe oyo nasala bango, na yango nazali kobanga été noki bakoboma ngai"
  26,15,"(Allah ayebisaki ye): Eloko ezali te, bökende bino mibale na bilembo bia biso, tokozala elongo na bino tozali koyoka"
  26,16,"Bökende epai ya falo bino mibale, boyebisa ye ete, Nkolo ya mokili nde atindi biso ya sólo"
  26,17,Mpo opesa biso bana ya isalayele
  26,18,"Falo alobi: Tobokoloki yo te kowuta bolenge?, mpe tovandaki nayo bamibu ebele te"
  26,19,"Мре osalaki maye osalaki, mpe ozalaki kati ya bapengwi"
  26,20,"Mûssa alobi: Nasalaki yango mpo été nazangaki koyeba"
  26,21,"Yango nakimaki bino тропа bobangi. Sima Nkolo wa ngai apesi ngai bwanya, mpe aponi ngai okati ya batindami"
  26,22,"Wana nde bolamu nayo ozali kokundolela ngai yango, mpe yo osili kozua bana ya isalayele bawumbu nayo"
  26,23,(Falo ) alobi; nani Nkolo wa molongo
  26,24,"(Mûssa) alobi: Nkolo wa likolo na mabele, na maye manso mazali otei na yango mibale, soki bozali na ntembe te"
  26,25,"Falo alobi na baye bazali pembeni naye ete: Boye bozali koyoka te"
  26,26,(Mûssa) alobi; Nkolo wa bino mpe Nkolo ya bato ya kala
  26,27,"(Falo) alobi: Ya soló motindami oyo batindi ye epai na bino azali ligboma"
  26,28,"(Mûssa) alobi: Nkolo wa moniele na eloli, na manso maye mazali otei na yango mibale. Soki bozali koyeba"
  26,29,"(Falo) alobi: Soki olandi nzambe mosusu otiki ngai, nakokotisa yo na boloko"
  26,30,"(Mûssa) alobi: Ata soki nayeli yo bikamwa ya polele"
  26,31,"(Falo) alobi: Yaka na yango soki ozali o kati ya balobi bosôló"
  26,32,"(Mûssa) abwaki lingenda lia ye, mpe tala ebongwani nyoka ya polele ebandi kotambola"
  26,33,"Mpe abimisi loboko naye na libenga, mpe tala ekomi pembe makasi pona baye bazali kotala"
  26,34,"(Falo) alobi na bankumu naye bazalaki pembeni naye: Ya soló, oyo nde nganga monene ya boyebi"
  26,35,"Alingi kobimisa bino o mabele na bino na bonganga naye, boye bokosala nini"
  26,36,"Balobi: Zelisa ye na ndeko wa ye, mpe tinda bato na mboka mpo basangisa (bakende kosangisa banganga, sima baya komekana)"
  26,37,Mpe bamemela yo banganga ya minene oyo bayebi
  26,38,Banganga basangani o mokolo mwa elaka
  26,39,"Mpe bayebisi na bato ete: Boye bokosangana te"
  26,40,Mpo tolanda banganga soki bango balongi
  26,41,"Mpe tango banganga bakomi epai ya falo balobi naye été: Boye tozali na lifuta soki tolongi"
  26,42,"(Falo) alobi: Iyo, ya soló, nakotiya bino pembeni na ngai"
  26,43,"Mûssa ayebisi bango: Bobwaka oyo bolingi kobwaka"
  26,44,"Mpe babwaki basinga na bamangenda na bango, (mpe balobi): Na nguya ya falo ya sólo, tokolonga"
  26,45,"Mpe Mûssa abwaki lingenda lia ye, mpe tala emeli nyoso oyo basalaki"
  26,46,Mpe banganga nyoso bakweyaki na kofukama
  26,47,"Balobi: Tondimi na Nkolo wa molongo"
  26,48,Nkolo ya Mûssa na Hânına
  26,49,"(Falo) alobi: Bondimi naye yambo ete napesa bino ndingisa! Ya sólo, ye nde mokonzi ya bino oyo alakisaki bino bonganga, bokoyeba kala te. Nakokata bino maboko na makolo na lolenge ya bokeseni, mpe nakobaka bino banso na nzete"
  26,50,"Banganga balobi: Mabe ezali te, pamba te, mpo tokozongaka ya soló epai ya Nkolo wa biso"
  26,51,"Ya soló, posa na biso ezali ete Nkolo wa biso alimbisa biso, mpo tozali bato ya yambo тропа kondima (ye Allah)"